         I don't know if this has been posted in the past 6 pages, but I have swapped HP items for a) affliction efficeiency and b) extended affliction focus items and would probably do so for a c) affliction haste focus effect item. </P><P>I don't regret it. </P><P>My goal is to get all 3 of these focus effects on items that also have hp, resists, mana and ac on them (in that order).</P><P>I see my willingness to dump HP for the focus effects as proof that the focus effects have been implemented with success (in that they are more useful than raw hp which used to be the most important stat).</P><P>Lich Futsau Strychnophillin of Morell-Thule Server<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
